{"tid":1761923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我而家日日都會睇幾份大公報","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T08:39:08.000Z","uid":133942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81da3e54a207b412d83636f9587a4d8e6f8dce9c","tid":1761923,"uid":133942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"我呢幾個月每次經過便利店就會拎起份大公報睇<br />\n由頭睇到尾<br />\n然後好想好整齊咁摺返埋放返原位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但次次都係摺撚到好似比人輪姦完咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死啦 如果個個都好似我咁睇大公報<br />\n咁咪份份都變撚哂垃圾咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9cbd248eb835c59e11eddf07acc35318b04afe","tid":1761923,"uid":133942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"}]}